songs.title: Stronger

description.plain: A stand out track from Theory of Reggaetivity, Stronger interpolates the quote “What doesn’t kill you, makes you stronger” into the Jamaican dialect. In this inspirational tune, Sasco encourages the listener to persevere through difficult times, using the tough experiences to gain wisdom and develop determination and patience that will ultimately contribute to their success.
